title: Liner Notes: Explore Bob Dylan's Blood on the Tracks in 4 Minutes
text: Now watching: Explore Bob Dylan's Blood on the Tracks in 4 Minutes Perhaps the most iconic breakup album of all time, Blood on the Tracks was both a return to form and unlike anything Bob Dylan had ever recorded before.
